        .featured-text.text-center.text-white.text-lg-left
          h4 Level 101 Studios, NYC
          p.text-white-50.mb-0
            | Was contacted by photographer Alain Joseph to create a website for his photography business. The idea was to showcase the depth and quality of the images into a series of galleries.
    // Project One Row
    .row.justify-content-center.no-gutters.mb-5.mb-lg-0
      .col-lg-6
        a(href='http://docuprosolutions.com/')
          img.img-fluid(src='/assets/img/portfolio/thumbnails/Docupro Solutions.png' alt='')
      .col-lg-6
        .bg-black.text-center.h-100.project
