        .bg-black.text-center.h-100.project
          .d-flex.h-100
            .project-text.w-100.my-auto.text-center.text-lg-right
              h4.text-white Recipe Locker
              p.mb-0.text-white-50
                | Web application that is built with Ruby on Rails. Used TDD during the entire build. Features Gravitar integration, Trix rich text editor, and user validations.
              hr.d-none.d-lg-block.mb-0.mr-0
    // Project Three Row
    .row.justify-content-center.no-gutters.mb-5.mb-lg-0
      .col-lg-6
        a(href='http://therestaurantreviewer.herokuapp.com/')
          img.img-fluid(src='/assets/img/portfolio/thumbnails/RestaurantReviewer.png' alt='')
      .col-lg-6
        .bg-black.text-center.h-100.project
          .d-flex.h-100
            .project-text.w-100.my-auto.text-center.text-lg-left
              h4.text-white Restaurant Reviewer
              p.mb-0.text-white-50
                | Web application that is built with Ruby on Rails. Features Login/Registration Validations, Google Map integration, &amp; the ability for users to leave a rating via the Ratyrate gem.
              hr.d-none.d-lg-block.mb-0.ml-0
    // Project Four Row
    .row.justify-content-center.no-gutters
      .col-lg-6
        a(href='https://github.com/ccoolawn/OnlineMarketplace')
