      .col-lg-6.order-lg-first
        .bg-black.text-center.h-100.project
          .d-flex.h-100
            .project-text.w-100.my-auto.text-center.text-lg-right
              h4.text-white Online Marketplace
              p.mb-0.text-white-50
                | Online Marketplace is an e-commerce application built with Ruby on Rails. This project uses the Stripe API for credit card processing. There is a seller dashboard that shows the number of products sold.
              hr.d-none.d-lg-block.mb-0.mr-0
    // Project Five Row
    .row.justify-content-center.no-gutters.mb-5.mb-lg-0
      .col-lg-6
        a(href='https://github.com/ccoolawn/Angular-Point-of-Sale')
