      .col-lg-6
        .bg-black.text-center.h-100.project
          .d-flex.h-100
            .project-text.w-100.my-auto.text-center.text-lg-left
              h4.text-white Angular POS (Point Of Sale)
              p.mb-0.text-white-50
                | A simple point of sale application built on the MEAN stack. SPA built with two views. One to add menu items, and one to calculate the subtotal &amp; Total including a tax rate of 7.5%.
              hr.d-none.d-lg-block.mb-0.ml-0
